and canada and lowash and metallurgical coal mines in the united states it serves silicone chemical aluminum and steel manufacturers auto companies and their suppliers ductile iron foundries manufacturers of photovoltaic solar cells and computer chips and concrete producers the company was formerly known as velonewco limited ferroglobe plc was incorporated in  and is headquartered in london the united kingdom ferroglobe plc is a subsidiary of grupo villar mir sa detailed description lansdowne housend floorwest wing berkeley squarelondon  wj erunited kingdomfounded in  employees phone     wwwferroglobecom key executives for ferroglobe plc mr francisco javier lópez madrid executive chairman age  total annual compensation m mr alan kestenbaum senior advisor age  total annual compensation m compensation as of fiscal year  ferroglobe plc key developments ferroglobe plc appoints deloitte llp as auditor jun   ferroglobe plc announced at the agm held on june   the shareholders appointed deloitte llp as auditor of the company to hold office from the conclusion of the annual general meeting until the conclusion of the next general meeting at which accounts are laid before the company ferroglobe plc annual general meeting jun   jun   ferroglobe plc annual general meeting jun   at  coordinated universal time location brown’s hotel  dover street london united kingdom agenda to approve the directors’ and auditor’s reports and the accounts of the company for the financial year ended  december  to consider the the directors’ remuneration report excluding that part containing the directors’ remuneration policy for the year ended  december  to consider the reelection of directors to appoint deloitte llp as auditor to hold office from the conclusion of the annual general meeting until the conclusion of the next general meeting to authorise the director to purchase own shares to authorise the company to make political donations and to consider the amendment of the company’s articles of